Arusha. Richard Gomes won the CMC Monthly Mug on Sunday following a 69 gross score at Arusha Gymkhana in Arusha.Gomes was playing off handicap-7 as he cruised into the victory, beating Korpela Daniel (handicap-2) who posed a big threat throughout the event.Daniel, one of the club s top players, scored 73 nett to settle for the second spot in the Division A. I played really good golf today and everything was just going right for me on the course, a delighted Gomes said. I am very happy with this title, there were a lot of brilliant golfers out there, but I thank God that I beat all of them, he said.The Division B title went to Neote Avatar Singh.